msgid "You can only register payment for posted journal entries."
msgstr "U kunt alleen de betaling registreren voor geposte journaalboekingen."

#. module: cyllo_accounting_pdc
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/cyllo_accounting_pdc/models/account_pdc_payment.py:0
#, python-format
msgid ""
"You can't create a new payment without an outstanding payments/receipts "
"account set either on the company or the %s payment method in the %s "
"journal."
msgstr ""
"U kunt geen nieuwe betaling maken zonder een uitstaande "
"betalingen/ontvangstenrekening die het bedrijf of de betaalmethode van %in "
"het %S Journal is ingesteld."

#. module: cyllo_accounting_pdc
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/cyllo_accounting_pdc/wizard/account_pdc_payment_register.py:0
#: code:addons/cyllo_accounting_pdc/wizard/account_pdc_payment_register.py:0
#, python-format
msgid ""
"You can't create payments for entries belonging to different companies."
msgstr ""
"U kunt geen betalingen maken voor inzendingen van verschillende bedrijven."

#. module: cyllo_accounting_pdc
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/cyllo_accounting_pdc/wizard/account_pdc_payment_register.py:0
#, python-format
msgid ""
"You can't open the register payment wizard without at least one "
"receivable/payable line."
msgstr ""
"U kunt de Wizard Register Payment niet openen zonder ten minste één "
"ontvangbare/te betalen lijn."

#. module: cyllo_accounting_pdc
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/cyllo_accounting_pdc/wizard/account_pdc_payment_register.py:0
#, python-format
msgid ""
"You can't register a payment because there is nothing left to pay on the "
"selected journal items."
msgstr ""
"U kunt geen betaling registreren omdat er niets meer is om te betalen op de "
"geselecteerde tijdschriftitems."

#. module: cyllo_accounting_pdc
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/cyllo_accounting_pdc/wizard/account_pdc_payment_register.py:0
#, python-format
msgid ""
"You can't register payments for journal items being either all inbound, "
"either all outbound."
msgstr ""
"U kunt geen betalingen registreren voor tijdschriftitems die allemaal "
"inkomen zijn, ofwel allemaal uitgaande."

